2011-11-25  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* common/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/common/objects/TvShow.java:
	  A TvShow can now store an instance of a Channel. Added getChannel() and
	  setChannel(Channel).

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/activities/tvsearch/TvSearch.java:
	  Create Jobs only for TvShows that support a Channel.

2011-11-25  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* common/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/common/utils/JobBuilder.java:
	  Added a method to get the list of created jobs.

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/util/JobRecorder.java:
	  New. This utility class should be used to send jobs to the server. The
	  Http request is prepared here and the response is parsed.

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/activities/tvguide/TvGuide.java:
	  Removed the code to send jobs to TvRecorder server. This code is placed in
	  JobRecorder now.

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/activities/tvguide/TvShowsAdapter.java:
	  Added a method that returns a list of TvShows that contains all TvShows
	  currently stored in the adapter.

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/activities/tvsearch/TvSearch.java:
	  Registered an options menu with two items: an item to record selected
	  TvShows and an item to record all TvShows currently displayed.

	* clients/android/res/values/strings.xml: Added strings for options menu
	  in the TvSearch Activity.

2011-11-25  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* server/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/server/rest/RecordServerResource.java:
	  This resource no longer throws IOExceptions for invalid jobs. All valid
	  jobs are used; the valid jobs are returned as JSONArray.

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/activities/tvguide/TvGuide.java:
	  Displays the number of jobs that have been successfully recorded.

2011-11-25  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/activities/tvguide/TvGuide.java:
	  Do not block the UI thread while sending new jobs to TvRecorder server.
	  Display error or info popups after Http traffic is finished.

	* clients/android/res/values/strings.xml: Added strings used to be
	  displayed while recording jobs from TvGuide.

2011-11-25  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/activities/tvjoblist/TvJoblist.java:
	  Display progress dialog while removing jobs and if an error occured.

	* clients/android/res/values/strings.xml: Added error and progress strings
	  for removing jobs.

2011-11-25  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/activities/tvjoblist/TvJoblistAdapter.java:
	  Added a method to remove a list of Jobs.

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/activities/tvjoblist/TvJoblist.java:
	  Added a context menu (on long press) with two options: remove the
	  selected job / remove all jobs.

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/data/JobProvider.java:
	  Added a method to remove a list of jobs. The jobs, that have been
	  removed is returned. This list can differ from the input list!

	* clients/android/res/values/strings.xml: Added strings for the
	  TvJoblist's context menu.

2011-11-25  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* server/docs/schema.sql: Added a further column 'atJobId_end' to store
	  the id of the at job which is used to stop a recording.

	* server/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/server/utils/AtJobRemover.java:
	  New. This class is used to remove at jobs.

	* common/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/common/utils/JSONUtils.java:
	  Added a function that transforms a list of jobs into a JSON array.

	* server/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/server/backend/Backend.java,
	  server/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/server/rest/JobListServerResource.java,
	  server/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/server/rest/RecordServerResource.java:
	  Improved process to remove at jobs. Also the id of the at job which is
	  used to stop a recording is stored in the database now. And both at jobs
	  are deleted when a Job is removed.

2011-11-24  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* server/docs/schema.sql: Added an integer field to job relation which
	  stores the at job id. This id is required to be able to delete jobs.

	* server/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/server/backend/Backend.java:
	  Added an integer atJobId to insertJob(). This integer is inserted to the
	  job relation now. In addition, there is a new method to find the atJobId
	  of a given Job.

	* server/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/server/utils/AtJobCreator.java:
	  Read the at job id from stdout.

	* server/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/server/rest/RecordServerResource.java:
	  Insert the at job id into database using insertJob(Job, int).

2011-11-22  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* server/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/server/rest/JobListServerResource.java:
	  Order Jobs based on their start time. Usually, this should be done in
	  clients, but we want to increase performance on this way.

2011-11-22  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* common/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/common/objects/Job.java:
	  Added setter methods for start and end time.

	* common/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/common/utils/DateUtils.java:
	  Fixed wrong time collision detection.

	* server/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/server/rest/RecordServerResource.java:
	  Prepare icoming Jobs: add 1 second to its start time to avoid collisions
	  with other jobs that end in the same minute.

2011-11-20  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/activities/tvjoblist/TvJoblist.java:
	  Display information for the case that no queued jobs exist and for the
	  case that the connection to the server failed.

	* clients/android/res/values/strings.xml: Added error and information
	  strings for the TvJoblist.

2011-11-20  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/activities/tvjoblist/TvJoblist.java:
	  Improved exception handling while fetching queued jobs. The Activity
	  will no longer crash when the server does not respond for any reason.

2011-11-20  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/activities/tvjoblist/TvJoblist.java:
	  Display a progress dialog while fetching queued jobs from server.

	* clients/android/res/values/strings.xml: Added strings used in the
	  progress dialog.

2011-11-20  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/android/res/layout/tvjob_list.xml: Improved the list layout.

2011-11-17  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/activities/tvjoblist/TvJoblist.java:
	  New. This activity displays all existing jobs in queue.
	  
	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/data/JobProvider.java:
	  New. This class should be used to fetch a list of queued jobs from
	  server.

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/activities/tvjoblist/TvJoblistAdapter.java:
	  New. An ArrayAdapter that is used for displaying Jobs in a ListView.

	* clients/android/res/layout/tvjob_list.xml,
	  clients/android/res/layout/tvjoblist.xml: New. Layout definitions for
	  the TvJoblist Activity and its ListView.

	* clients/android/AndroidManifest.xml: Registered the TvJoblist Activity.

	* clients/android/res/values/strings.xml: Added a title for the TvJoblist
	  Activity.

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/MainMenu.java:
	  Defined an OnClickListener that start the TvJoblist Activity.

	* common/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/common/utils/JSONUtils.java:
	  Added functions to parse Jobs or a list of Jobs from
	  JSONArray/JSONObject.

	* server/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/server/rest/JobListServerResource.java:
	  This resource now returns a StringRepresentation with a JSON string now.
	  The JsonRepresentation could not be read on the Android client.

2011-11-17  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/android/res/layout/menu.xml: Added a button to enter the (not
	  existing) joblist activity.

	* clients/android/res/values/strings.xml: Added a title for the joblist
	  menu button.

	* clients/android/res/drawable/joblist_button.png: New. An icon for the
	  joblist menu button.

	* clients/android/res/layout/main.xml: Removed. It was initially created
	  at project start and never used.

2011-11-17  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* common/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/common/utils/DateUtils.java:
	  Removed Log4J logger which is not usable on Android platforms.

	* common/pom.xml: Removed Apache log4j dependency.

2011-11-17  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* common/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/common/rest/JobListResource.java,
	  server/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/server/rest/JobListServerResource.java:
	  New. This resource implements the HTTP GET operation which will return a
	  JsonRepresentation with jobs that are marked to be recorded.

	* server/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/server/rest/RestApp.java:
	  Registered the JobListServerResource.

2011-11-16  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo@intevation.de>

	* common/pom.xml: Added dependency to Apache log4j.

	* common/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/common/utils/DateUtils.java:
	  Improved collision detection.

	* server/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/server/rest/RecordServerResource.java:
	  Improved collision detection of time.

	* server/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/server/utils/StartAtJobCreator.java:
	  Replace whitespaces in job files.

2011-10-31  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/client/modules/ManualModule.java:
	  Load Channels from TvGuideService - removed TvGuideFaker.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/shared/TvGuideFaker.java:
	  Removed. We are able to fetch TvGuide information from TvRecorder server
	  now.

2011-10-31  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/shared/DateUtils.java:
	  New. This utility class is used to work with dates in GWT clients.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/client/widgets/TvShowCell.java:
	  Display start and end of a TvShow.

2011-10-26  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/client/widgets/TvShowCell.java:
	  Subclasses GWT's AbstractCell now. The layout stuff is done by native
	  html elements instead of using SmartGWT widgets which is a lot faster.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/client/modules/TvGuideModule.java:
	  The TvShows of each Channel are displayed in CellList provided by GWT
	  that consists of TvShowCells.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/webapp/TvRecorder.css: Adapted styles for
	  TvShowCell.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/client/widgets/ChannelColumn.java:
	  Deleted.

2011-10-26  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/gwt/pom.xml: Added a dependency to Restlet.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/web.xml: Added context-params for
	  user and password. Both parameters are used for Http BasicAuth if
	  required by TvRecorder server.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/server/HttpClient.java:
	  New. This class is used to handle Http traffic between this WWW client
	  and the TvRecorder server.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/server/TvRecorderService.java:
	  New. This service should be the parent of all RPC services used in this
	  client. It provides some basic methods for Http traffic.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/server/TvGuideServiceImpl.java:
	  Now subclasses TvRecorderService and implements the getTvGuide() method.
	  The TvGuide is fetched from TvRecorder server via Http using HttpClient.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/shared/JSONHelper.java:
	  New. A helper class for working with JSON strings/objects.

2011-10-24  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/client/TvRecorder.java:
	  Added the TvGuideService as static member.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/client/services/TvGuideService.java,
	  clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/client/services/TvGuideServiceAsync.java,
	  clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/server/TvGuideServiceImpl.java:
	  New. A RPC service that is used to fetch TvGuide information from
	  TvRecorder server.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/client/modules/TvGuideModule.java:
	  Read TvGuide (Channels with TvShows) from TvGuideService.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/server/Log4JInitServlet.java:
	  New. A servlet that is used to initialize Log4J logging.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/shared/model/DefaultChannel.java,
	  clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/shared/model/DefaultTvShow.java:
	  Added empty constructors required by GWT.

	* clients/gwt/pom.xml: Added a dependency to Log4J.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/log4j.properties: New. A Log4J
	  properties file.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/web.xml: Registered the
	  TvGuideService and Log4JInitServlet. The Log4JInitServlet is called
	  initially to setup Log4J logging.

2011-10-24  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/client/modules/AbstractModule.java:
	  Implements Stateful. Changing the selection of a module will change its
	  style.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/client/modules/TvRecorderModuleList.java:
	  Mark selected modules (AbstractModule.setSelected(true)) and deselect
	  previously selected modules.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/client/widgets/TvShowCell.java:
	  Implements Stateful now.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/webapp/TvRecorder.css: Added a style for a selected
	  AbstractModule.

2011-10-24  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/client/widgets/ChannelColumn.java:
	  New. A ChannelColumn inherits from VLayout. It renders all TvShows of a
	  Channel in vertical order with the help of TvShowCells.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/client/widgets/TvShowCell.java:
	  New. A TvShowCell renders the most important information (title, start,
	  end, length, category, description) in a VLayout. A TvShowCell implements
	  Stateful.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/client/widgets/Stateful.java:
	  New. This interface is used to mark classes having a state (selected, not
	  selected).

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/client/modules/TvGuideModule.java:
	  Implemented doRender() which now creates a HLayout with ChannelColumn.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/webapp/TvRecorder.css: Added styles for TvShowCell
	  and ChannelColumn.

2011-10-24  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* .hgignore: Ignore 'clients/gwt/target' directory.

2011-10-21  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/shared/model/Channel.java,
	  clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/shared/model/DefaultChannel.java:
	  New. A Channel and its default implementation used in the GWT client.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/shared/model/TvShow.java,
	  clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/shared/model/DefaultTvShow.java:
	  New. A TvShow and its default implementation used in the GWT client.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/shared/TvGuideFaker.java:
	  New. The TvGuideFaker implements a method that returns a static list of
	  Channels with or without static TvShows. This class is used until the
	  REST services of this client are ready so that we are able to fetch
	  Channels and TvShows from TvRecorder server.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/client/modules/ManualModule.java:
	  Use TvGuideFaker.getChannels() to retrieve a list of Channels instead of
	  creating Channels manually.

2011-10-21  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/client/widgets/TButton.java:
	  New. This text button shoud be used around the whole application.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/webapp/TvRecorder.css: Added styles for the
	  TButton.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/client/modules/ManualModule.java:
	  Implemented an inital view of this module. It contains text fields for
	  entering start and end date/time, the output name, a listbox that
	  displays the availabe channels and a button bar to create a new Job and
	  to reset the view.

	* clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/shared/model/Channel.java,
	  clients/gwt/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/gwt/shared/model/DefaultChannel.java:
	  The Channel interface used around this client and its default
	  implementation.

2011-10-21  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/gwt/README.txt,
