2011-10-12  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/activities/tvsearch/TvSearch.java:
	  New. Activity that displays a list with all TvShows and an editable
	  textfield. The textfield might be used to filter the TvShow list.

	* clients/android/res/layout/menu.xml: Added  a menu button for the TvSearch
	  activity.

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/MainMenu.java: Start
	  TvSearch Activity if its button was pressed.

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/activities/tvguide/TvShowsAdapter.java:
	  Made it more robust to support empty TvShow lists.

	* clients/android/res/layout/tvsearch.xml: New. The layout description of
	  TvSearch.

	* clients/android/res/drawable/search_button.png: New. TvSearch icon for
	  the main menu.

	* clients/android/AndroidManifest.xml: Registered the new TvSearch
	  Activity.

	* clients/android/res/values/strings.xml: New strings for the TvSearch
	  Activity.

2011-10-12  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	=== RELEASE 0.2 ====

	* NEWS: Prepared NEWS for release 0.2

2011-10-12  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/activities/tvguide/TvGuide.java:
	  Bugfix: Allow HTTP traffic and force synchronization of TvGuide when the
	  user selects the "update" item in the options menu.

2011-10-12  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/activities/tvguide/TvGuideDataStore.java:
	  Add notification when we have fetched new TvGuide information from HTTP
	  server.

	* clients/android/res/values/strings.xml: Added strings used in the
	  notification bar.

2011-10-11  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/activities/tvguide/TvGuideDataStore.java:
	  Added the option to fetch TvGuide information from database only - which
	  means to suppress HTTP traffic.

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/activities/tvguide/TvGuide.java:
	  HTTP traffic is suppressed while fetching TvGuide information when the UI
	  is created initially. The user still has the option to update the TvGuide
	  himself by selecting the "update" item in the options menu.

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/receivers/TvGuideUpdateReceiver.java:
	  Adapted the TvGuideDataStore.get() call to allow HTTP traffic.

2011-10-10  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/android/res/layout/tvshowdetail.xml: Display 'category' and
	  'length' and the start and end time of a TvShow. Furthermore, there is
	  an ImageView at the left top corner that might be used to display images
	  for a TvShow. If there is no image specified, we will display
	  'tvdetail_no_image.png'.

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/activities/tvguide/TvShowsAdapter.java,
	  clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/activities/tvshow/TvShowDetail.java:
	  Set 'category' and 'length' information of TvShows.

	* common/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/common/utils/DateUtils.java:
	  Added a new formatter string that displays the name of the week day
	  besides the date.

	* clients/android/res/values/strings.xml: New string used as suffix for
	  the datetime string in the TvShowDetail activity.

	* clients/android/res/drawable/tvdetail_no_image.png: New image that is
	  used in the TvShowDetail activity. It is displayed if there is no image
	  specified for a TvShow.

	* clients/android/res/values/colors.xml: New resource file where colors
	  should be specified.

2011-10-10  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/database/ChannelSQLiteHelper.java,
	  clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/database/SQLiteProvider.java:
	  Prepared sqlite database and sqlite helper class to support 'category'
	  and 'length' of TvShows.

2011-10-06  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* common/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/common/utils/JobBuilder.java:
	  New. This builder helps creating new record Jobs. There are methods to
	  add Jobs and to write out the collected Jobs to JSONArray.

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/activities/tvguide/TvGuide.java:
	  Make use of the JobBuilder to create the required JSONArray for
	  recording selected jobs.

2011-10-06  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* server/conf/log4j.properties: Modified the layout pattern: write the
	  classname to log only - do not write the fully qualified name (with
	  package names).

	* server/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/server/rest/RecordServerResource.java:
	  Added some more debug output in the collision detection for new jobs.

2011-10-06  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* server/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/server/rest/RecordServerResource.java:
	  Improvded this resource to be able to record a list of jobs. It will now
	  accept a JSONObject representing a single Job or a JSONArray which
	  represents a list of JSONObject representing single jobs.

2011-10-06  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* common/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/common/objects/TvShow.java: A
	  TvShow can now have a category and a length (which is not specified by its
	  start and end time).

	* server/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/server/tvguide/xmltv/XmlTvShowUpdater.java:
	  Read category and length from XmlTv file while parsing TvShows.

	* common/src/main/java/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/common/utils/JSONUtils.java:
	  Take category and length of TvShows into account while reading/writing
	  TvShows from/to JSON representation.

2011-10-05  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* server/contrib/epgloader/otr/otrparser.py: Parse category and length of
	  a program.

	* server/contrib/epgloader/model.py: Added constructor arguments for
	  category and length.

	* server/contrib/epgloader/xmltv/xmltvexporter.py: Write out category and
	  length of programs.

2011-10-05  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* server/contrib/epgloader/epgdownload.py: Added command line options for
	  start and end date.

2011-09-28  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* .hgignore: Ignore .pyc files.

2011-09-28  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* server/contrib/epgloader/__init__.py,
	  server/contrib/epgloader/epgdownload.py: A python tool for reading EPG
	  data from different sources (currently, only OTR is supported) and
	  writing those information to different formats (currently, only XmlTv is
	  supported). Use "epgdownload.py --help" to get more information about
	  how to use this tool.

	* server/contrib/epgloader/epgparser.py: The interface description of an
	  EPG parser. The intent of epgparser is to provide multiple parsers for
	  different EPG sources.

	* server/contrib/epgloader/exporter.py: The interface description of an
	  EPG exporter. The intent of an exporter is to support different formats
	  for storing EPG information.

	* server/contrib/epgloader/model.py: Provides classes used for
	  reading/writing EPG information.

	* server/contrib/epgloader/otr/__init__.py,
	  server/contrib/epgloader/otr/otrparser.py: A concrete epgparser that
	  allows reading EPG data from OTR (www.onlinetvrecorder.com).

	* server/contrib/epgloader/xmltv/__init__.py,
	  server/contrib/epgloader/xmltv/xmltvexporter.py: A concrete exporter
	  that allows writing channels and programs to an xmltv file.

	* server/README: Added Python2.6 and Python-lxml dependencies.

2011-09-20  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/android/res/layout/tvguide_list.xml: Added a column to select /
	  unselect a TvShow by using a checkbox.

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/activities/tvguide/TvShowsAdapter.java:
	  Save a boolean value for each TvShow provided by the adapter. Selected
	  TvShows might be received using the getSelectedTvShows() method.

	* clients/android/src/de/inselhome/tvrecorder/client/activities/tvguide/TvGuide.java:
	  The TvGuide no longer supports a context menu by long press on a
	  specific TvShow. The context menu has been replaced by an
	  OnClickListener that starts the TvShowDetail Activity for showing
	  TvShows details and a further option menu item that triggers a process
	  to record all selected TvShows.

	  NOTE: Currently, the process to record the selected TvShows is not
	  implemented as well as the server doesn't support recording more than a
	  single job at once.

	* clients/android/res/values/strings.xml: Added a button string for
	  recording selected TvShows.

2011-09-14  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/android/icons/icon.xcf: New. The gimp template of the icon that
	  is used as launcher icon.

	* clients/android/res/drawable-hdpi/icon.png,
	  clients/android/res/drawable-ldpi/icon.png,
	  clients/android/res/drawable-mdpi/icon.png: New. Icons in different
	  sizes for the launcher.

2011-09-14  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/android/res/layout/tvrecorder.xml: Improved the layout - added
	  some margins for a better usage of space.

2011-09-14  Ingo Weinzierl <ingo_weinzierl@web.de>

	* clients/android/res/drawable-land/main_menu_button.png,
	  clients/android/res/drawable-land/main_menu_button_pressed.png,
	  clients/android/res/drawable-land/main_menu_button_state.xml,
	  clients/android/res/drawable-land/settings_button.png,
	  clients/android/res/drawable-land/tvguide_button.png,
	  clients/android/res/drawable-land/tvrecorder_button.png: Copied from
	  res/drawable.

	* clients/android/res/layout-land/menu.xml,
	  clients/android/res/layout-land/tvrecorder.xml: New. Layout definitions
	  for the main menu and the tvrecorder activities in landscape mode.

